### NotionChartKit API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Get all datasets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/datasets

### Get all charts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/charts

### Create dataset (will fail - no user/connection exists)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/datasets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Test Dataset",
  "databaseId": "notion-db-id-123",
  "connectionId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "config": {
    "databaseId": "notion-db-id-123",
    "groupBy": "status",
    "aggregationType": "count"
  },
  "refreshIntervalMinutes": 60
}

### Create dataset (validation error - missing required fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/datasets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Dataset"
}

### Create chart (will fail - no dataset exists)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/charts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "datasetId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "type": "bar",
  "metadata": {
    "title": "My Chart",
    "xAxisLabel": "Category",
    "yAxisLabel": "Count"
  },
  "isPublic": true
}

### Get specific chart (will fail - no chart exists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/charts/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
